target: Great! What day and time to you want to travel on?
context: <user>  I'm looking for a place to stay while in Cambridge. What is available in the west area that has free wifi? <system>  There are 4 hotels to choose from. I can recommend Finches Bed and Breakfast. It's a cheap 4 star guesthouse. Does that work? <user>  I need a guesthouse with a star rating of 0. <system>  I'm sorry, there are no 0 star guesthouses, would you like to try something else? <user>  Is there a guesthouse located in the centre with free wifi? <system>  El Shaddai fits your needs. Would you like me to reserve a room? <user>  Does that have free parking? <system>  Yes it does. It's cheap and has free parking.<user>  Thanks for the info. I also need to look for a train. Can you look that up? <system>  Absolutely. Let me start by asking you what your departure and destination locations will be?<user>  I'm going from Cambridge to Ely. <system>
